1
00:00:00,060 --> 00:00:02,060
[Episode 16]

2
00:00:02,060 --> 00:00:03,090
Yours

3
00:00:13,130 --> 00:00:14,570
What do you want now, huh?

4
00:00:16,250 --> 00:00:20,580
I give my bed partners full marks
as a way to show respect

5
00:00:22,530 --> 00:00:26,090
You should also
be a bit polite like this

6
00:00:30,290 --> 00:00:36,290
I don't think so
since last time only you came

7
00:00:37,450 --> 00:00:41,410
I didn't come
so I can't give full marks

8
00:00:46,460 --> 00:00:50,650
Wait
that's our university tie

9
00:00:51,450 --> 00:00:53,310
Did you sneak in here in disguise?

10
00:00:54,290 --> 00:01:00,770
No, because last time we were accused
of causing a disturbance here

11
00:01:01,570 --> 00:01:05,489
So they don't allow
anyone except students to enter

12
00:01:07,690 --> 00:01:09,060
Don't tell me

13
00:01:10,210 --> 00:01:14,270
You paid tuition for your bodyguard too
so he could come to school with you

14
00:01:15,930 --> 00:01:19,530
Taji, he's just
borrowing my clothes

15
00:01:21,690 --> 00:01:23,350
Just admit you're in disguise

16
00:01:26,170 --> 00:01:29,810
So why are you following me?
Is there something you need?

17
00:01:31,810 --> 00:01:37,610
I'm not following you
I just transferred here

18
00:01:38,009 --> 00:01:40,330
If he knew the person he likes

19
00:01:40,330 --> 00:01:42,650
Was the acne-covered person
he hated most as a child

20
00:01:42,650 --> 00:01:44,050
How would he feel?

21
00:01:45,289 --> 00:01:49,770
Could it be... you have a crush on me?

22
00:01:55,650 --> 00:02:00,330
I like... sleeping with you, I guess

23
00:02:09,030 --> 00:02:14,310
Don't change the subject
You haven't answered me. How will you take responsibility?

24
00:02:16,450 --> 00:02:20,110
How do you want me to take responsibility?
Do you want me to pay you?

25
00:02:21,090 --> 00:02:22,810
I'm not a prostitute

26
00:02:39,450 --> 00:02:43,140
Isn't that the person who put
a black plastic bag over my head?

27
00:02:43,140 --> 00:02:45,720
[To Be Continued]
